{
  "texts": [
    "This hybrid approach balances topical representativeness with phenomenological richness.",
    "The third approach employed Sentence-BERT (SBERT) with Maximal Marginal Relevance (MMR) for embeddingbased sentence selection.",
    "SBERT generates dense semantic embeddings using transformer encoders [23].",
    "MMR iteratively selects sentences by balancing document relevance and diversity [24].",
    "Relevance is computed against a document embedding, while diversity penalizes redundancy among selected sentences."
  ]
}